OL,3,CGold toilet stolen from Blenheim
OL,4,CPalace in 'audacious raid', court hears
OL,6,FAn "audacious raid" was carried out to
OL,7,Fsteal a #2.8 million gold toilet from
OL,8,FBlenheim Palace, a court has heard.
OL,10,FIt is believed that the distinctive
OL,11,Ffully functioning toilet, entitled
OL,12,F'America', which had been installed as
OL,13,Fan artwork at the Oxfordshire country
OL,14,Fhouse where Sir Winston Churchill was
OL,15,Fborn, has now been split up and
OL,16,Fdisposed of, Oxford Crown Court was
OL,17,Ftold.
