OL,3,CGold toilet stolen from Blenheim
OL,4,CPalace in 'audacious raid', court hears
OL,6,FThe toilet, which was created by
OL,7,FItalian artist Maurizio Cattelan, was
OL,8,Fa star attraction in an exhibition
OL,9,Fwhen it was stolen by sledgehammer-
OL,10,Fwielding thieves who smashed their way
OL,11,Finto the palace.
OL,13,FProsecutor Julian Christopher KC said
OL,14,Fthe raid took just five minutes,
OL,15,Fadding: "This case concerns the theft
OL,16,Fof a work of art from Blenheim Palace
OL,17,Fin September 2019.
OL,19,F"It was an unusual work of art, being
OL,20,Fa fully functioning toilet made of 18
OL,21,Fcarat gold, entitled America.
