OL,3,CGold toilet stolen from Blenheim
OL,4,CPalace in 'audacious raid', court hears
OL,6,F"It weighed approximately 98kg and was
OL,7,Finsured for the sum of six million
OL,8,Fdollars (#4.75 million)
OL,10,F"The gold it was made from was itself
OL,11,Fworth in the region of #2.8 million at
OL,12,Fthe time."
OL,14,FMichael Jones, 39, from Oxford,
OL,15,Fpleaded not guilty in January to
OL,16,Fstealing artwork in an overnight raid
OL,17,Fin the early hours of September 14
OL,18,F2019.
