OL,4,CPalace in 'audacious raid', court hears
OL,6,FFrederick Sines, 36, also known as
OL,7,FFrederick Doe, of Winkfield, Windsor,
OL,8,FBerkshire, and Bora Guccuk, 41, from
OL,9,Fwest London, each deny one count of
OL,10,Fconspiracy to transfer criminal
OL,11,Fproperty.
OL,13,FThe court heard that the sledgehammers
OL,14,Fwere left at the scene.
OL,16,FA photograph was taken about 17 hours
OL,17,Fbefore the toilet was stolen and the
OL,18,Fprosecution allege that Jones had
OL,19,Ftaken it while he was "there as part
OL,20,Fof the reconnaissance for the
OL,21,Fburglary".
