OL,11,FIt is alleged that Doe and Guccuk
OL,12,Fagreed to help one of the men who
OL,13,Fcarried out the burglary ` a defendant
OL,14,Fcalled James Sheen ` to sell some of
OL,15,Fthe gold in the following weeks.
OL,17,FJurors were told that a fourth
OL,18,Fdefendant, Sheen, 40, from
OL,19,FWellingborough, Northamptonshire, has
OL,20,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to burglary.
